title: Don’t Mess With This Ninja Turtle! (TMNT) 🐢 #shorts
description:
Special thanks to @paramountpictures for sponsoring this short!

Which Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtle has the BEST weapon: Donnie, Raph, Mickey, or Leo? With Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles: Mutant Mayhem  releasing only in theatres August 2nd, we had to ask. Would the katanas, bo staff, sai, or nunchaku win in a fight? Grab a slice of pizza and let’s fight this thing out. Cowabunga, Loyal Theorists!
